    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just hard to talk to people about it because they don't get it. they just want to fix the \"sadness,\" but it's not sadness. it's just the truth. the person they liked, the one who actually had value, isn't here. what's even the point of trying to \"feel better\" when the person who was supposed to feel those things is gone? it feels like i'm just pretending to be alive.",
