    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so heavy. like, every single day is just this massive performance of being someone i'm not, just to keep everyone else from being disappointed. but if i'm already dead inside... why am i still doing the work of staying here? it feels like i'm just haunting my own life.",
